.name
CCC
.fullname
Crunch Crumble Chomp
.type
Shoot Em Up Game
.short
Destroy a large city with your monster
.description
You guide a monster on its career of trashing a large city. Your
objective; to destroy as much of the city as possible before your
monster is destroyed by the military. The game is keyboard
controlled for one player.
Choice of monsters and different weapon types.
This is an update from version 0.2 to 0.8
.version
0.9
.date
1995.3.1
.author
Ronald F. Picardi
.restrictions
Save game not available. Game exits to Workbench when your
monster is destroyed. Some bugs may be present.
.requirements
Any Amiga with 1 meg or more memory.
.distribution
Shareware
.address
630 Bacon Rd
Saginaw, MI 48609
.construction
Compiled AmosPro
.tested
A500, A600, A2000, CD32-SX1, A4000/40
